snippet.title: Indian Summer üçÇ A Warm Jazz Hug for You and Your Little One üí§
snippet.description:
Some afternoons feel like they are meant for slowing down. The light gets softer, the air grows still, and everything quiets. Indian Summer comes from that feeling. It is a warm and gentle jazz lullaby, created to bring a sense of peace to your baby and to you.

We hope it brings you a moment to breathe, dream, and simply be. üí§üçÇ

‚ú¨ ABOUT US ‚ú¨

We are Mu Dimon and Rubio Faviere, the musicians behind Songs of Birdland. We record and produce all the music and videos you see in our own studio, with great dedication and a deep love for jazz and classical music. Every piece is an original creation made for all of you :)
